<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٩٠-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنِي حَرْبٌ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُ أَحْمَدَ قُلْتُ: رَجُلٌ تَصَدَّقَ بِصَدَقَةٍ ثُمَّ وَرِثَهَا؟<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> لَا بَأْسَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>